  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-1)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2-6x-7)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-1)^2+(x^2-6x-7)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-1=0 (1) \\\\x^2-6x-7=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-1=0\\)\n\\((x-1)(x+1)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2-6x-7=0\\)\n\\(D=36+28=64\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{6-8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-1\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{6+8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=7\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-1)(x+1)=0 \\\\x=-1; x=7\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=1; x=-1 \\\\x=-1; x=7\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-1\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-1\\)",
